metadata.name: Genetic change of a flower
metadata.description:
Aster is an ancient bloom that has been around for thousands of years, and you better believe itâ€™s got a story to tell.
Definitely, in these long years, a genetic mutation has occurred and a girl was born from the cool and fresh star flower. Her parents do not have human faces or bodies. Their communication is all through the petals and hair of their daughter.   Maybe you are seeing the first blue-haired girl of the ancient world!   Wherever she walks, more flowers and branches grow and cover her body to Avoid danger. A dress made of leaves has a feeling of vitality and a wild world.
The girl with blue hair is called Robin. Technically, she has A deep personality. Everyone in FLOWERLAND has agreed that she is generally a confident person, however. She always loves music, As listening to music makes her grow. ðŸŒ±
